text: Enjoy their steamed chicken instead of the fried chicken. It comes with brown rice too.
Tried the steamed chicken w brown rice.  Really fresh tender chicken, and soft fuffy brown rice... seriously delicious!

The signs don't keep up with the rate at which prices are being increased; ate here as I read the stall being recommended. Definitely a solid fried chicken, though freshness of leaves is meh and tofu lacks some flavor.
Overall decent meal for the price, but perhaps doesn't live up to its good old days?
I tried steamed chicken rice for the first time and the taste was delicious!

My order when Iâ€™m there is the chicken wing rice. For just over four dollars, it is very value for money. The chicken wing is flavourful, with a slightly thicker crisp coating than normal. However, this gives it a nice crunch. This dish is served with curry rice.

Do request for "nasi lemak" chili as it elevates the flavour profile of the chicken and cuts through the oiliness too.
